<div class="article-header article-header-full">
	<h1 itemprop="headline ">8 Ways to Cope With Mean Girls</h1>
		<div class="subtitle">What to tell your daughter when she faces a mean girl</div>
</div>

<div class="article-header-default row">
	<div class="col col-10 col-pc-10 col-tablet-7">


<div class="by-line by-line-inline ">
	
	<div class="">
					    <a href="http://bullying.about.com/bio/Sherri-Gordon-102617.htm" data-component="byLineDefault" data-source="Bio" data-type="authorId" data-ordinal="1" class="by-line-author-img"><img data-original="http://f.tqn.com/d/g/bw/102617.gif" width="50" height="50" data-load="lazy" /></a>
